The paper explores the practicality of applying neural style transfer as an emerging design tool for generating creative digital content. This involves using deep learning algorithms to create artistic visual variations of digital content. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.GR (Graphics), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
